They were revered for their wisdom and power and were often called upon to perform healing rituals or interpret dreams. In many cultures, Shamanism was considered the first form of religion, and shamans were considered the spiritual leaders of their communities.

Today, Shamanic Spheres is a team of music composers who specialize in creating music that embodies the shamanic spirit. Their music is intended to connect listeners with the spiritual realm and to help them access the power and wisdom of the shamanic tradition.
